### Upload de documents
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="documents[]"; filename="facture.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./chemin/vers/facture.pdf
--WebAppBoundary--

### Liste des documents
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/documents

### Créer une alerte
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/alertes
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "type": "siren_mismatch",
    "niveau": "rouge",
    "message": "SIREN différent entre facture #1 et attestation #2",
    "documents_concerenes": [1, 2],
    "details": {"sirens": ["123456789", "987654321"]}
}

### Vérifier des documents
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/verifier/documents
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "document_ids": [1, 2, 3]
}